title: Lady Gang Doctor
overview: A young doctor arrives in a quiet rural town. Ryoko Kanzaki, 24 years old, is the daughter of legendary surgeon Yuji Kanzaki.  Crushed by the weight of expectations, she rebelled in her youth and became a delinquent. Against all odds, she earned her medical license and now finds herself assigned to Southern Cross Hospital â€” the very place where her father once worked. But her new beginning won't be as simple as she hopes...
